  <note reference-line="7" id="1">
    <original>samādiṇṇāni (sī. ka.)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet>‘‘Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, catasso komāriyo pajāpatiyo ahesuṃ. Atha khvāhaṃ, bhante, yena tā pajāpatiyo tenupasaṅkamiṃ; upasaṅkamitvā tā pajāpatiyo etadavacaṃ – ‘mayā kho, bhaginiyo, brahmacariyapañcamāni sikkhāpadāni samādinnāni </snippet>
    <match>samādinnāni</match>
